title: Ergebnisse der Exakten Naturwissenschaften
additional-notes: This is a German publication. Its contents may still be copyrighted even without renewals or copyright notices, if they meet GATT copyright restoration requirements for works first published outside the US. Some volumes may also mention New York as a publisher location, however.
